The paper presents an algorithm for finding integer vectors that satisfy a certain condition, which involves linear algebra and computational geometry. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the numerical analysis (cs.NA), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), computational complexity (cs.CC), computational geometry (cs.CG), and scientific computing (cs.SC) sub-categories.
